<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>Bootstrap Example</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jquery@3.5.1/dist/jquery.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <style>
        /* Make the image fully responsive */

       body{
           background: linear-gradient(270deg, rgba(100,107,128,0.5) 0%, rgba(146,218,231,0.5)100%);
           color: black;
       }
        .carousel-inner img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .information-part {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .checked {
            color: orange;
        }

        .review-container {
            width: 300px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;

        }

        .review-container h4 {
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-size: medium;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        .description {
            margin-top: 10px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .pay-btn{
            position: absolute;
            width: 80%;
            bottom: 20px;
            left: 100px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: lightblue;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .pay-btn a{
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .pay-btn a:hover{
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .pay-btn:hover{
            background: linear-gradient(270deg, rgba(100,107,128,0.5) 100%, rgba(146,218,231,0.5) 0%);
        }

        .carousel-item{
            width: 100%;
            height: 300px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        .corDiv{
            height: 600px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <%- include('../partials/navbar') -%>
   
    <div id="demo" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" >

        <!-- Indicators -->
        <ul class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#demo" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#demo" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#demo" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        </ul>

        <!-- The slideshow -->
        <div class="carousel-inner corDiv img-fluid">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/da/Taj-Mahal.jpg" alt="Los Angeles" width="100%" height="400px">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="https://natureconservancy-h.assetsadobe.com/is/image/content/dam/tnc/nature/en/photos/Zugpsitze_mountain.jpg?crop=0,176,3008,1654&wid=4000&hei=2200&scl=0.752" alt="Chicago" width="100%" height="100%">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="https://natureconservancy-h.assetsadobe.com/is/image/content/dam/tnc/nature/en/photos/Zugpsitze_mountain.jpg?crop=0,176,3008,1654&wid=4000&hei=2200&scl=0.752" alt="New York" width="100%" height="100%">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Left and right controls -->
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#demo" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon"></span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#demo" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon"></span>
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="information-part">
        <h3>Taj Mahal, Agra</h2>
        <div class="review-container">
            <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
            <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
            <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
            <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
            <span class="fa fa-star"></span>
            <h4>295 reviews</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Quos officiis natus aspernatur? Cum accusamus,
            nulla debitis quas, dolores fugit esse, odit modi numquam deserunt deleniti! Nihil, sit, cum odio
            aspernatur, fuga labore consequuntur aut unde corrupti quia voluptatem placeat esse assumenda deserunt rerum
            quo culpa odit illo excepturi at. Magni, delectus! Aut rerum earum dolorem sunt facilis tempora quia atque
            esse incidunt placeat praesentium eius officia deserunt ratione impedit nemo iure iusto ipsa ut, rem
            blanditiis molestias! Quod nisi magnam est accusantium mollitia. Temporibus maxime in recusandae, aspernatur
            dolorum alias. <a href="">read more</a>
        </div>
        <div class="pay-btn">
            <a href="/form">Proceed to buy</a>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>